    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for a <strong>holiday adventure</strong> packed with fun alongside <strong>Tim</strong> and <strong>Spooky</strong>! Guide these cheeky furballs through 90 jolly levels where you'll tackle <strong>Match 3 puzzles</strong> to help Tim snag his frosty fish treats and assist Spooky in tracking down Christmas gift boxes. <strong>Suddenly Meow Christmas</strong> features a hilarious storyline set in Grandma's house, where you'll help spruce up her living room and <strong>save it from a cat-astrophe</strong>! Plus, enjoy hidden object challenges and quirky minigames that amp up the festive fun. Perfect for cat lovers and puzzle fans, this whimsical game is your ticket to a merry escape this Christmas season. Join the furry frolic and make magical holiday memories!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >90 Match 3 levels to conquer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Humorous Christmas story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save Grandma's living room.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden objects and other minigames.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect stars to prove your mastery.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many more challenges.</p></li></ul>",
